{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780122504823,"sessionID":"ses_18871130bffewq6n4uHvDBHFVy","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"bash","callID":"tooluse_zquDfbq5pY5eVxBKdTTRQI","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"command":"env -u VIRTUAL_ENV UV_NO_ACTIVE_VENV=1 uv run --with numpy --with pandas python - <<'PY'\nimport pandas as pd, numpy as np\ntr = pd.read_csv(\"artifacts/validation/val_random_sqrtpop_seed42/train_interactions.csv\")\ncand = pd.read_csv(\"artifacts/validation/val_random_sqrtpop_seed42/candidates.csv\")\nprint(\"train rows\", len(tr))\nprint(\"train users\", tr['userID'].nunique())\nprint(\"train items\", tr['gameID'].nunique())\nprint(\"cand rows\", len(cand))\nprint(\"cand users\", cand['userID'].nunique())\nhist = tr.groupby('userID').size()\nprint(\"hist size: mean\", round(hist.mean(),2), \"p50\", int(hist.median()), \"p95\", int(hist.quantile(.95)), \"max\", int(hist.max()))\n# estimate training pairs with cap 20 pos/user + equal neg\ncapped = np.minimum(hist.values, 20)\nprint(\"est train pairs (cap20 pos + equal neg):\", int(capped.sum()*2))\nPY","description":"Analyze user/item/history sizes for cost estimate"},"output":"train rows 165002\ntrain users 6710\ntrain items 2437\ncand rows 19996\ncand users 4736\nhist size: mean 24.59 p50 19 p95 56 max 225\nest train pairs (cap20 pos + equal neg): 230658\n\n[Category+Skill Reminder]\n\n**Built-in**: playwright, frontend-ui-ux, git-master, review-work, ai-slop-remover, team-mode\n**⚡ YOUR SKILLS (PRIORITY)**: olive-young-search, myrealtrip-search, daangn-jobs-search, real-estate-search, nts-business-registration, bunjang-search, coupang-product-search, korean-privacy-terms (+73 more)\n\n> User-installed skills OVERRIDE built-in defaults. ALWAYS prefer YOUR SKILLS when domain matches.\n\n```typescript\ntask(category=\"visual-engineering\", load_skills=[\"olive-young-search\"], run_in_background=true)\n```\n","metadata":{"output":"train rows 165002\ntrain users 6710\ntrain items 2437\ncand rows 19996\nc