{"type":"text","timestamp":1780123330169,"sessionID":"ses_18871130bffewq6n4uHvDBHFVy","part":{"id":"prt_e779e30ff0010uAvjm1q9eSt9a","messageID":"msg_e779e1276001KNgSBfrzy4RBpy","sessionID":"ses_18871130bffewq6n4uHvDBHFVy","type":"text","text":"This single-line docstring is necessary (priority 3): `FeatureConfig` is the central abstraction of the bug fix — its entire reason for existing is to guarantee one config drives both candidate and training-pair features. The docstring states that invariant, which is not obvious from the field names alone. Keeping it.\n\nNow Edit 2 — add the BM25 time-decay variant to `add_time_decay_graph_scores`. The matrix is recency-weighted, then BM25-weighted, then cosine item-item sim, then per-user top-3 mean (matching Stage2). I'll add a small helper that computes top-3 sim scores from a precomputed similarity matrix.","time":{"start":1780123316479,"end":1780123330145}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1780123330260,"sessionID":"ses_18871130bffewq6n4uHvDBHFVy","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"edit","callID":"tooluse_b3ZwGJxQyw9aUNAn8JmToC","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py","newString":"def itemknn_top3_from_sim(sim: np.ndarray, X: sp.csr_matrix, candidates: pd.DataFrame, user_to_idx: dict[str, int], item_to_idx: dict[str, int]) -> np.ndarray:\n    score_top3 = np.zeros(len(candidates), dtype=np.float32)\n    for n, (uid, gid) in enumerate(candidates[[\"userID\", \"gameID\"]].itertuples(index=False)):\n        ui = user_to_idx.get(str(uid))\n        gi = item_to_idx.get(str(gid))\n        if ui is None or gi is None:\n            continue\n        hist = X.indices[X.indptr[ui] : X.indptr[ui + 1]]\n        if hist.size == 0:\n            continue\n        vals = sim[gi, hist]\n        k = min(3, vals.size)\n        score_top3[n] = float(np.partition(vals, -k)[-k:].mean())\n    return score_top3\n\n\ndef add_time_decay_graph_scores(train_df: pd.DataFrame, scored: pd.DataFrame, half_lives: list[int], ease_half_life: int, ease_lambda: float) -> tuple[pd.DataFrame, dict[str, object]]:\n    out = scored.copy()\n    user_to_idx, item_to_idx, _, _ = build_maps(train_df)\n    meta: dict[str, object] = {\"half_lives\": half_lives, \"ease_half_life\": ease_half_life, \"ease_lambda\": ease_lambda}\n    for hl in half_lives:\n        weights = recency_weights(train_df, hl)\n        X = build_sparse_matrix(train_df, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, values=weights)\n        ssum, stop3 = cosine_itemknn_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx)\n        out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_sum\"] = ssum\n        out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_top3\"] = stop3\n        X_bm25 = bm25_weight(X)\n        sim_bm25 = compute_item_similarity(X_bm25)\n        out[f\"score_time_itemknn_bm25_hl{hl}_top3\"] = itemknn_top3_from_sim(sim_bm25, X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx)\n        if hl == ease_half_life:\n            out[f\"score_time_ease_hl{hl}_lambda{ease_lambda:g}\"] = ease_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, ease_lambda)\n        meta[f\"hl{hl}_matrix_nnz\"] = int(X.nnz)\n    return out, meta","oldString":"def add_time_decay_graph_scores(train_df: pd.DataFrame, scored: pd.DataFrame, half_lives: list[int], ease_half_life: int, ease_lambda: float) -> tuple[pd.DataFrame, dict[str, object]]:\n    out = scored.copy()\n    user_to_idx, item_to_idx, _, _ = build_maps(train_df)\n    meta: dict[str, object] = {\"half_lives\": half_lives, \"ease_half_life\": ease_half_life, \"ease_lambda\": ease_lambda}\n    for hl in half_lives:\n        weights = recency_weights(train_df, hl)\n        X = build_sparse_matrix(train_df, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, values=weights)\n        ssum, stop3 = cosine_itemknn_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx)\n        out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_sum\"] = ssum\n        out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_top3\"] = stop3\n        if hl == ease_half_life:\n            out[f\"score_time_ease_hl{hl}_lambda{ease_lambda:g}\"] = ease_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, ease_lambda)\n        meta[f\"hl{hl}_matrix_nnz\"] = int(X.nnz)\n    return out, meta"},"output":"Edit applied successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"diff":"Index: /opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py\n===================================================================\n--- /opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py\n+++ /opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py\n@@ -514,8 +514,24 @@\n             out[n] = float(user_scores[ui, gi])\n     return out\n \n \n+def itemknn_top3_from_sim(sim: np.ndarray, X: sp.csr_matrix, candidates: pd.DataFrame, user_to_idx: dict[str, int], item_to_idx: dict[str, int]) -> np.ndarray:\n+    score_top3 = np.zeros(len(candidates), dtype=np.float32)\n+    for n, (uid, gid) in enumerate(candidates[[\"userID\", \"gameID\"]].itertuples(index=False)):\n+        ui = user_to_idx.get(str(uid))\n+        gi = item_to_idx.get(str(gid))\n+        if ui is None or gi is None:\n+            continue\n+        hist = X.indices[X.indptr[ui] : X.indptr[ui + 1]]\n+        if hist.size == 0:\n+            continue\n+        vals = sim[gi, hist]\n+        k = min(3, vals.size)\n+        score_top3[n] = float(np.partition(vals, -k)[-k:].mean())\n+    return score_top3\n+\n+\n def add_time_decay_graph_scores(train_df: pd.DataFrame, scored: pd.DataFrame, half_lives: list[int], ease_half_life: int, ease_lambda: float) -> tuple[pd.DataFrame, dict[str, object]]:\n     out = scored.copy()\n     user_to_idx, item_to_idx, _, _ = build_maps(train_df)\n     meta: dict[str, object] = {\"half_lives\": half_lives, \"ease_half_life\": ease_half_life, \"ease_lambda\": ease_lambda}\n@@ -524,8 +540,11 @@\n         X = build_sparse_matrix(train_df, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, values=weights)\n         ssum, stop3 = cosine_itemknn_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx)\n         out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_sum\"] = ssum\n         out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_top3\"] = stop3\n+        X_bm25 = bm25_weight(X)\n+        sim_bm25 = compute_item_similarity(X_bm25)\n+        out[f\"score_time_itemknn_bm25_hl{hl}_top3\"] = itemknn_top3_from_sim(sim_bm25, X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx)\n         if hl == ease_half_life:\n             out[f\"score_time_ease_hl{hl}_lambda{ease_lambda:g}\"] = ease_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, ease_lambda)\n         meta[f\"hl{hl}_matrix_nnz\"] = int(X.nnz)\n     return out, meta\n","filediff":{"file":"/opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py","patch":"Index: /opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py\n===================================================================\n--- /opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py\n+++ /opt/data/kaggle/kmu-rec-sys-26-steam/scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py\n@@ -514,8 +514,24 @@\n             out[n] = float(user_scores[ui, gi])\n     return out\n \n \n+def itemknn_top3_from_sim(sim: np.ndarray, X: sp.csr_matrix, candidates: pd.DataFrame, user_to_idx: dict[str, int], item_to_idx: dict[str, int]) -> np.ndarray:\n+    score_top3 = np.zeros(len(candidates), dtype=np.float32)\n+    for n, (uid, gid) in enumerate(candidates[[\"userID\", \"gameID\"]].itertuples(index=False)):\n+        ui = user_to_idx.get(str(uid))\n+        gi = item_to_idx.get(str(gid))\n+        if ui is None or gi is None:\n+            continue\n+        hist = X.indices[X.indptr[ui] : X.indptr[ui + 1]]\n+        if hist.size == 0:\n+            continue\n+        vals = sim[gi, hist]\n+        k = min(3, vals.size)\n+        score_top3[n] = float(np.partition(vals, -k)[-k:].mean())\n+    return score_top3\n+\n+\n def add_time_decay_graph_scores(train_df: pd.DataFrame, scored: pd.DataFrame, half_lives: list[int], ease_half_life: int, ease_lambda: float) -> tuple[pd.DataFrame, dict[str, object]]:\n     out = scored.copy()\n     user_to_idx, item_to_idx, _, _ = build_maps(train_df)\n     meta: dict[str, object] = {\"half_lives\": half_lives, \"ease_half_life\": ease_half_life, \"ease_lambda\": ease_lambda}\n@@ -524,8 +540,11 @@\n         X = build_sparse_matrix(train_df, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, values=weights)\n         ssum, stop3 = cosine_itemknn_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx)\n         out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_sum\"] = ssum\n         out[f\"score_time_itemknn_hl{hl}_top3\"] = stop3\n+        X_bm25 = bm25_weight(X)\n+        sim_bm25 = compute_item_similarity(X_bm25)\n+        out[f\"score_time_itemknn_bm25_hl{hl}_top3\"] = itemknn_top3_from_sim(sim_bm25, X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx)\n         if hl == ease_half_life:\n             out[f\"score_time_ease_hl{hl}_lambda{ease_lambda:g}\"] = ease_scores(X, out, user_to_idx, item_to_idx, ease_lambda)\n         meta[f\"hl{hl}_matrix_nnz\"] = int(X.nnz)\n     return out, meta\n","additions":19,"deletions":0},"truncated":false},"title":"scripts/paper_guided_next_steps.py","time":{"start":1780123330181,"end":1780123330257}},"id":"prt_e779e664a001i8LWe4KG3RXm2Y","sessionID":"ses_18871130bffewq6n4uHvDBHFVy","messageID":"msg_e779e1276001KNgSBfrzy4RBpy"}}
